      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle boasts a flawless aesthetic profile and mechanical integrity that remains beyond reproach. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as a premier investment-grade asset. For the individual who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents the definitive choice in the pre-owned luxury market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
