    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a private collection. This car has been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed monthly, resulting in a mirror-finish exterior completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains that 'new car' aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history from the original dealership. With such low mileage and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key opportunity for a discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best. It looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
