    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to really appreciate how pristine it is. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
