    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 in pristine Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, delivering linear power through a precision 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically, this M3 is superlative: the rod bearings have been proactively addressed, and the Double VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals. The rear subframe\u2014a known structural point\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity during spirited cornering. The suspension retains its original factory geometry with zero bushing deflection, and the limited-slip differential operates silently with perfect lockup. With concours-level paint depth and a completely stock powertrain, this is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically transparent, turn-key example of the ultimate analog driving machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
